Class Ball

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.shape.Shape
        • javafx.scene.shape.Circle
          • Ball
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget

    class Ball
extends javafx.scene.shape.Circle
    Ball class is used to display circles on the grid for the game. It inherits from Circle which is non-serializable class. Hence, the need for the SerializableBall class.
    Author:
    Meet Arora
